### 4.2 — Liveness Detection (VULN-08)

#### [MODIFY] [face.py](file:///d:/mindkraft/Team-A-Frontend/Team-A-Backend/Team-A-Backend/app/services/face.py)

Add multi-frame variance check:

```python
def _check_liveness(descriptors: list[list[float]], min_frames: int = 3) -> bool:
    """Ensure descriptors have natural variance (not a static photo)."""
    if len(descriptors) < min_frames:
        return False
    # Calculate pairwise variance — real faces have micro-movements
    variances = []
    for i in range(len(descriptors) - 1):
        dist = _euclidean_distance(descriptors[i], descriptors[i + 1])
        variances.append(dist)
    avg_variance = sum(variances) / len(variances)
    # Real faces: 0.01-0.15 variance between frames
    # Photos: < 0.005 (static) or > 0.3 (completely different)
    return 0.005 < avg_variance < 0.30
```

